    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个健康科技的数据流图。核心是从患者记录开始，经过HIPAA合规的数据保险库，最后到达诊断引擎。这三个节点要串联起来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。方向是从患者记录流向保险库，再流向诊断引擎吗？还是双向的？另外节点B和C的命名我直接用HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault和HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，单向流动，从A到B再到C。命名就用全称，保持业务语义清晰。患者记录是入口，HIPAA保险库做合规中转，诊断引擎做最终分析。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画第一版：三个节点从上到下排列，A连B，B连C。用TB纵向布局，这样数据流向比较直观。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我看你画的B和C之间好像没有箭头？另外A到B的连接也需要明确标注流向。我们这是合规系统，必须清晰展示数据是怎么从患者记录进入诊断引擎的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下：A→B→C，三条连接都加上箭头。这样患者记录流向HIPAA保险库，再流向诊断引擎，流程完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再确认下节点B的定位——HIPAA保险库不只是存储，它还要做脱敏和审计日志。不过图上不用展开这些细节，保持三层结构简洁。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整完毕。最终结构：HealthTech_PatientRecords在最上，中间是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，底部是HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，单向箭头串联。TB纵向布局，符合你的描述。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
